Description











                                          Description
                                      






Red Sox former first basemen George Scott has personally hand-signed this MLB baseball and inscribed it 8x GG-During his major league baseball career George Scott played for four teams which included the Boston Red Sox, Milwaukee Brewers, Kansas City Royals and New York Yankees. He is more famously known with his time as being a member of the Boston Red Sox, known for his good sense of humor in his 14 year career he was a three-time All-Star (1966, 1975, 1977), hit over 20 homeruns six times in
 his career and was an eight-time Gold Glove Award winner. This George Scott Autograph is guaranteed authentic and includes a Steiner Sports Certificate of Authenticity and an accompanying tamper-evident Steiner Hologram.




































