Banded Crescent
Art Glass Sculpture
(ID: A33948)

Created by
George Scott



 Limited Edition


    Assembly of this piece is a many step process. First, small glass pieces are stacked and cast into a slab. The slab is then sliced into sections, which are trimmed to size and then  cast again into a crescent form. Finally, the crescent is ground and polished and then fired once more. Every inch of this piece contains amazing patterns, with each individual layer of glass interacting with its neighbors. Reflected and transmitted light allow for many varied display opportunities. Limited edition of 5.






Shipping Information



